name: Carbonite Chamber Console (V)
Lore: 'Most often used to freeze Tibanna gas for transport. Modified by Ugloste to work on humans. Intended to capture Luke Skywalker, the Emperor''s prize.',
Text: 'Deploy on Carbonite Chamber. Once per game may use 3 Force to to take [Virtual Block 6][Jabba''s Palace] Boba Fett into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. While Jabba''s Prize on Tatooine, you may add 1 to your destiny draws in battle anywhere, and once per game may take into hand Audience Chamber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to Sabotage and Uutkik.',
